description:
The crack team responsible for creating inspiring and epic dioramas for the Warhammer World Exhibition Hall gave us a behind-the-scenes peek at the latest, featuring a fierce battle between Stormcast Eternals and Skaven within the Gnaw. Learn more about the Warhammer Age of Sigmar display:  https://www.warhammer-community.com/2024/07/26/the-stormcast-eternals-hold-the-line-in-this-towering-new-warhammer-world-diorama/
